name: Figs with Bacon & Chile
description: It's made with roasted fresh figs tossed in maple syrup, a touch of Cinnamon, Thyme, Garlic, Balsamic vinegar and olive oil. IT'S SUPER FLAVORFUL!.

name: Phyllo Cup
description: Phyllo cups are light, buttery and extra flaky. Now you can make restaurant-ready-looking appetizers and desserts easily at home. Fill them with almost anything; sweet or savory

name: Al Lago wines
description: Taste our premier vine and enjoy the views, fell in love with a breath taking places.

name: Mushroom puff
description: This crispy, bite size mushroom puffs are perfect snack or appetizer. The bites with gruyere and mustard are crowd pleasing appetizer perfect for parties and holidays.

name: Cedar-Plank salmon
description: Cedar-plank salmon is a fish delicacy that involves cooking salmon on cedar planks, a unique method of cooking which is believed to have been originally practiced by Native Americans who mostly used Western red cedar (a type of cypress).

name: Braised Chicken legs
description: Braised Chicken Legs: Tender, succulent, and full of flavor. Seared to perfection, slow-braised in aromatic herbs and spices, these chicken legs offer a tantalizing experience. Each bite unveils a harmonious blend of moist tenderness and rich, robust sauce. A culinary delight that promises a memorable dining experience.

name: Seared scallops
description: Seared Scallops: Golden-brown perfection meets oceanic sweetness. Delicately seared for a crispy exterior, these succulent treasures burst with elegant flavors. A visual and culinary masterpiece, offering an unforgettable taste of the sea.

name: Grilled Coconut Shrimp
description: Grilled Coconut Shrimp: Juicy shrimp, kissed by the grill and coated in tropical coconut goodness. A harmony of smoky flavors and sweet succulence that transports you to a beachside paradise. Unleash the taste of the tropics on your plate.

name: Chocolate Sheet Cake
description: Chocolate Sheet Cake: A cocoa lover's paradise. Moist, velvety cake cloaked in luscious chocolate ganache. Each bite a symphony of indulgence, a perfect harmony of flavors and textures. Elevate your dessert experience with pure chocolate decadence.

name: Caramel Pretzel Skillet
description: Caramel Pretzel Skillet: A harmony of gooey caramel and golden pretzel crunch. Sweet meets salty in a tempting dance of flavors and textures. Indulge in a captivating dessert experience that satisfies your cravings for both.

name: Mint Oreo Cake
description: Mint Oreo Cake: Refreshing mint-infused layers meet chocolatey Oreo crunch. Elegantly finished with velvety mint frosting. A divine balance of cool, rich, and delightful, redefining dessert indulgence.

name: Gooey Brownies
description: Gooey Brownies. These indulgent squares are a symphony of fudgy richness and irresistible sweetness. With every bite, you'll succumb to the luscious gooey center, a dessert masterpiece that ignites cravings and satisfies chocolate lovers' dreams.

name: Seabreeze Cocktail
description: Seabreeze Cocktail. A tantalizing fusion of vodka, cranberry, and grapefruit, perfectly balanced to transport you to sandy shores and sun-kissed waves. Refreshing, invigorating, and a sip of pure relaxation.

name: Triple Berry Sparklers
description: Triple Berry Sparklers. A dazzling medley of strawberries, blueberries, and raspberries, mingling harmoniously in effervescent splendor. Each sip is a burst of vibrant flavors, a celebration of fruity indulgence that ignites your taste buds.

name: Milk Shake
description: Milkshake. Velvety smoothness meets tantalizing flavors, creating a sip-worthy treat that transports you to dessert paradise. Satisfy your cravings with each luscious, refreshing gulp.

name: Stawberry Lemonade
description: Strawberry Lemonade. A symphony of flavors that dances on your palate, quenching your thirst with a delightful burst of tangy-sweet refreshment. A sip of sunshine that captures the essence of summer in every glass.

name: Potato Skin Bites
description: Potato Skin Bites. Crispy potato skins, perfectly seasoned and loaded with mouthwatering toppings. Each bite is a burst of savory delight, a tantalizing treat that redefines comfort food.

name: Beef Enchiladas
description: Beef Enchiladas: Tender shredded beef, seasoned to perfection, wrapped in soft tortillas and smothered in zesty enchilada sauce. A satisfying blend of spices and textures, creating a hearty dish that embodies the essence of Mexican cuisine.

name: Tiramisu Sundae
description: The classic creamy, coffee-soaked Italian dessert is transformed into a frosty layered sundae.

name: Basil Lemonade
description: A unique blend of lemonade and muddled basil leaves, offering a hint of herbal sophistication.

name: Bruschetta
description: Toasted baguette slices topped with diced tomatoes, garlic, basil, and a hint of olive oil.
